<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>新挖矿微信二维码 - GitHub Pages</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f8f8 0%, #e0e7ff 100%);
            color: #333;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 30px;
        }
        
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #07c160; /* 微信绿 */
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .emoji-text {
            font-size: 3rem;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .description {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .qr-section {
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f7ff 0%, #e6ffe6 100%);
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 2px dashed #07c160;
        }
        
        .qr-code {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #07c160;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .qr-label {
            color: #07c160;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        
        .github-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #07c160 0%, #06a85c 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .github-link:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06a85c 0%, #058b4f 100%);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(7, 193, 96, 0.2);
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                max-width: 100%;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .qr-code {
                width: 180px;
                height: 180px;
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="emoji-text">😀😀😀😀</div>
            <h1>测试成功</h1>
            
            <p class="description">
                这是通过老孙修改的页面，我编辑了他<br>
                GitHub Pages 部署成功！
            </p>
            
            <div class="qr-section">
                <div class="qr-code">
                    QR
                </div>
                <p class="qr-label">微信扫码即可访问</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>仓库地址：https://github.com/0tah-mitos/new-mine-WeiXinQR</p>
            
            <a href="https://github.com/0tah-mitos/new-mine-WeiXinQR" class="github-link">
                查看 GitHub 仓库
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Powered by GitHub Pages • Made with ❤️</p>
            <p>页面可实时编辑和更新</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>